      Cradle is a sci-fi first-person-view quest designed for  the player
      to explore the surrounding world. The  story is  built  around  the
      relations of the protagonist and a mechanical girl who by  quirk of
      fate found themselves amidst the desert.  The players  task  is  to
      repair the mechanical body of his companion and solve  the  mystery
      of the neglected entertainment park located not far from  the  yurt
      together.

      For more infos go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/361550/
